snippet.title: Phi - Official Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the Phi trailer for this 3D puzzle platformer game where emotions guide your journey. Play as PHI and navigate through 4 unique, emotion-inspired puzzles. Each level represents a powerful emotion, leading towards the hidden truth. Phi is currently slated for release in 2026 on PC, PS5, and Nintendo Switch. 

You can learn more about Phi on the game's Kickstarter page if you're interested: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/kyrelphi/phi-a-mystery-driven-game-filled-with-emotions.

#PHI #Kickstarter #Gaming
